omy and we should expect it to continue to\ndevelop richer structure, with room for different types of agents and\nmechanisms to coexist.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2007 12:09:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-09-04"}
